title: House centrists to unveil bipartisan border and aid deal for Ukraine and Israel
description: Centrist lawmakers plan to release their own bill to provide military aid to Ukraine, Israel and Taiwan along with some border provisions.

title: Gazan doctor reunited with family after Khan Younis hospital evacuation
description: Dr. Mohammed Harara had no contact with his family for several weeks while he worked non-stop to save lives in the collapsing Gazan medical system. “I can’t explain how I feel,” he told the NBC News crew who filmed the happy reunion. “Alhamdulillah (Thank God), they are fine and they are still alive,” he added.

title: Video shows scenes of chaos and destruction inside Gaza's Nasser Hospital
description: Eyewitness video from inside the Nasser Hospital in Khan Younis captured chaos, fear, smoke-filled corridors and the sound of gunfire as Israeli special forces prepared to launch a raid.

title: Australian prime minister gets engaged on Valentine's Day
description: Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese announced his engagement to partner Jodie Haydon, having proposed the night before on Valentine's Day. Albanese is the first prime minister to get engaged while in office, Australian media reported.

title: Doctor treats wounded in Rafah after evacuation ordered of the Nasser Hospital in Khan Younis
description: An NBC News crew encountered Dr. Mohammad Harara, who usually works at the Nasser Hospital in Khan Younis, providing aid to a wounded man in Rafah after Israel ordered the evacuation of the Nasser Hospital.

title: WATCH: Russia's Putin expresses preference for Biden as president
description: In an interview with Russian state television, President Vladimir Putin said that Russia would prefer to see President Joe Biden win a second term, describing him as more experienced than Donald Trump.

title: ‘She said yes’: Australian prime minister proposes to partner on Valentine’s Day
description: Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese celebrated Valentine’s Day by proposing to his partner, Jodie Haydon.

title: Israel launches airstrikes on Lebanon following rocket attack
description: Israel responded to a rocket barrage fired from Lebanon into northern Israel on Wednesday with a series of deadly airstrikes inside Lebanon. NBC News' Chapman Bell reports for Early Today.

title: Two Chinese fishermen drown after chase with Taiwan’s coast guard
description: Two Chinese fishermen drowned while being chased by Taiwan’s Coast Guard off the coast of Taiwan’s Kinmen archipelago, the coast guard said Wednesday.
